 identify their career goals and to categorize what they need to accomplish to achieve those goals  There is evidence that the IDP process also facilitates communication between faculty mentors and their trainees UIC Institutional Policy on the Use of Individual Development Plans  Resources  Resources for the preparation and review of Individual Development Plans are available at myIDP myIDP        n n nSponsored Programs n n n Sponsored Programs Preparing a Proposal Developing a Proposal Guidance for Categorizing Sponsored Project Activity Types Basic Procedures ORS Required Documents for Proposals Standard Institutional Information Electronic Portals Grants gov Proposal Central Sponsor Specific Information NIH NSF How to request an NSF Fastlane Account Other Agencies Developing a Budget Rates Budget Templates Using Less Than Full F A Routing to ORS What Routing Forms to Use  Post Submission Actions Just In Time Submission Procedures Supplemental Material Award Contract Processing   Acceptance Receiving your sponsored Research Award Contract Negotiating the Award Contract Common Problematic Terms Finalizing   Signatures Issuance of Subcontract and or Consultant Agreements PHS Subrecipient Compliance Export Controls Award Administration Prior Approval Guidance FDP Prior Approval Matrix NIH Prior Approval Instructions NIH Prior Approval Request Non Competing Progress Reports NIH Non Competing Progress Reports NSF Non Competing Progress Reports Grant Transfer Award Closeout myResearch Portal ORSWeb Forms   Contract Templates Policies Education   Training OMB Uniform Guidance I m Looking for Find Contacts Proposal Submission Award Negotiation Contact ORS                       awards uic edu awards uic edu  Illinois       Staff directory Subscribe to ORS Listserv Subscribe to ORS Listserv UIC Office of the Vice Chancellor for Research OVCR Main Office     Administrative Office Building  AOB  nMC     n     West Polk Street nChicago  IL       T               F            